ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in Nunavut (Kivalliq area) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN NUNAVUT (KIVALLIQ AREA) ORDER in order to repeal the existing Withdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in Nunavut (Kivalliq area) Order, made by P.c. 2016-374 of May 20, 2016, and to make a new Withdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in Nunavut (Kivalliq area) Order, pursuant to paragraph 23(a) of the Territorial Lands Act.
